OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1780600263
OL,3,C'Significant progress' in tackling
OL,4,Csome of NI's longest waiting times
OL,6,FNew figures from the Department of
OL,7,FHealth show waiting lists in Northern
OL,8,FIreland have fallen slightly, but all
OL,9,Fhealth trusts are still missing
OL,10,Fofficial waiting time targets.
OL,12,FMore than 500,000 people were waiting
OL,13,Ffor a first outpatient appointment at
OL,14,Fthe end of March 2026, down 3% on the
OL,15,Fprevious quarter.
OL,17,FInpatient and diagnostic waiting lists
OL,18,Fhave also improved, although more than
OL,19,Fhalf of outpatients were still waiting
OL,20,Fover a year to be seen.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
