OL,3,C'Significant progress' in tackling
OL,4,Csome of NI's longest waiting times
OL,6,FThree-year-old Eden Baxter is about to
OL,7,Fundergo a short procedure that could
OL,8,Fmake a big difference to her hearing.
OL,10,FAfter just eight weeks on the waiting
OL,11,Flist, she is heading into theatre for
OL,12,Fear vent surgery.
OL,14,FEden's Mum Abbie Rosbotham said: "I
OL,15,Fthink we have been through a course of
OL,16,Fabout six antibiotics from January.
OL,18,F"It was an urgency this time because
OL,19,Fnone of the antibiotics were actually
OL,20,Fclearing it for her".
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
