OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1780600263
OL,3,C'Significant progress' in tackling
OL,4,Csome of NI's longest waiting times
OL,6,FFor many parents, getting children
OL,7,Fseen and treated by Ear Nose and
OL,8,FThroat (ENT) services has involved
OL,9,Fmonths and sometimes years, of waiting.
OL,11,FAccording to the Department of Health,
OL,12,Fthat is now changing.
OL,14,FStaff at the Royal Victoria Hospital's
OL,15,Fpaediatric ENT ward said a sustained
OL,16,Feffort to increase capacity and tackle
OL,17,Fbacklogs is starting to make a
OL,18,Fdifference.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1780600263
OL,3,C'Significant progress' in tackling
OL,4,Csome of NI's longest waiting times
OL,6,F"Coming out of 2022, our waiting times
OL,7,Ffor common ENT surgeries for children,
OL,8,Fsuch as tonsillectomies were around
OL,9,Ffour years.
OL,11,F"We felt that was too much. We have
OL,12,Frun extra theatre lists, we have
OL,13,Fmaximised the theatres we have got and
OL,14,Fwe have been doing waiting list
OL,15,Fvalidation.
OL,17,F"A combination of all those factors
OL,18,Fover the past number of years,
OL,19,Fparticularly the last year, has
OL,20,Fbrought the waiting time down to
OL,21,Faround 6 months.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
