PN,44505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1780600263
OL,3,C'Significant progress' in tackling
OL,4,Csome of NI's longest waiting times
OL,6,F"Although it is not perfect, it is a
OL,7,Fsubstantial reduction", Conor Jackson
OL,8,FPaediatric ENT surgeon said.
OL,10,FPaediatric ENT is just one area where
OL,11,Fhealth officials say waiting times are
OL,12,Fbeginning to improve.
OL,14,FNew figures show the number of people
OL,15,Fwaiting for a first hospital
OL,16,Fappointment has fallen for the second
OL,17,Fquarter in a row.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
