FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1780600263
OL,3,C'Significant progress' in tackling
OL,4,Csome of NI's longest waiting times
OL,6,FMore than 385,000 additional
OL,7,Fassessments, tests and treatments were
OL,8,Fdelivered across Northern Ireland
OL,9,Fduring the last year, with some of the
OL,10,Flongest waiting lists for care falling
OL,11,Fsignificantly.
OL,13,F"We were given a challenge of four
OL,14,Fyear waits in various areas and nearly
OL,15,Fall of those have achieved 100%
OL,16,Freduction.
OL,18,F"Four years is still far too long, but
OL,19,Fthat was only the start ", Professor
OL,20,FMark Taylor, Regional Clinical
OL,21,FDirector for Elective Care said.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1780600263
OL,3,C'Significant progress' in tackling
OL,4,Csome of NI's longest waiting times
OL,6,FQuestions remain as to whether
OL,7,Fprogress can be sustained without
OL,8,Fpermanent reform.
OL,10,F"Simply putting a sticking plaster on
OL,11,Fto the waiting lists by using
OL,12,Fadditional money year on year -
OL,13,Fwithout changing the way we reform our
OL,14,Fhealth service - we would end up, when
OL,15,Fthat money dries up, (with) the
OL,16,Fwaiting lists coming back again,"
OL,17,FProfessor Taylor added.
